data.description: This one is a must see!!  From the moment you walk in you will be blown away!  As you enter you are greeted by a bright open living room flowing with Southern Pine flooring.  You will fall in love with the  remodeled modern kitchen fully equipped with new appliances, cabinets, butcher block countertops, farmers sink and island.  The upstairs bedrooms all have bench seats in the windows to allow for extra light and character. Downstairs is another huge bedroom, bright family room with fireplace, laundry room (yes, washer and dryer stay!) and another bedroom. The whole house has been freshly painted, new flooring throughout, bathrooms completely remodeled, new modern railing, new doors, new hardware and new trim throughout.  All you have to do is move in and enjoy!  Outside you have a fully fenced yard, raised gardens and the pool is staying!  With the covered deck, you can enjoy those summer bbq's watching the kids play!  There truly is something for everyone in this home! Centrally located near CSU-P, schools and shopping!  Take a look before it's gone!
